OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FIn response to Starmer's declaration
OL,6,Fof independence from Trump in relation
OL,7,Fto the Iran war - his refusal to join
OL,8,Foffensive strikes against the Islamic
OL,9,Ftheocracy - his ministerial colleagues
OL,10,Fare both reassured and anxious.
OL,12,F"It's landed quite well with the
OL,13,Fpublic, don't you think?" one said to
OL,14,Fme.
OL,16,FOpinion polls would corroborate,
OL,17,Fnamely, that a majority of British
OL,18,Fpeople are relieved we are not formal
OL,19,Fparticipants in the attacks on Iran
OL,20,Fitself.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FAnd although it is not comfortable for
OL,6,Fmany to hear an American president
OL,7,Fdenigrate a British prime minister as
OL,8,FTrump does daily at the moment, the
OL,9,Foperational co-operation between
OL,10,FBritish and US military and
OL,11,Fintelligence has not been impaired -
OL,12,For at least not yet.
OL,14,FThat is what I am told by officials
OL,15,Fwhose only skin in this game is
OL,16,FBritish security, and who have no
OL,17,Fpolitical reason to shore up Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FHowever, after two and a half weeks of
OL,6,Fthe Trump and Israeli-induced chaos
OL,7,Fengulfing the Middle East, the impact
OL,8,Fon our daily lives is not yet tangible
OL,9,F- but will be soon enough.
OL,11,FSenior members of the government
OL,12,Fbelieve, like me, financial and
OL,13,Fcommodity markets are under-pricing
OL,14,Fthe severity of the impact of Iran's
OL,15,Fde facto closure of the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz, the vital supply waterway for
OL,17,Foil, gas, fertiliser, helium and so on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FThe point, as one minister put it to
OL,6,Fme, is that tankers that left the Gulf
OL,7,Fshortly before the war started on 28
OL,8,FFebruary have not yet arrived in
OL,9,FEurope, because passage takes between
OL,10,Fthree and five weeks, depending on
OL,11,Ftheir size.
OL,13,FSo Europe has not yet experienced any
OL,14,Fdisruption to physical supplies. But
OL,15,Fthat shock to energy and other
OL,16,Fsupplies is about to hit, and will
OL,17,Fendure for many weeks, probably months
OL,18,F- even if, against all evidence, Trump
OL,19,Fis able to claim something he can semi-
OL,20,Fplausibly describe as victory any time
OL,21,Fsoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FApart from anything else, the threat
OL,6,Ffrom Iranian drones and mines in the
OL,7,FStrait probably won't vanish, even if
OL,8,FTrump declares his peace, because it
OL,9,Fis not at all clear that Tehran has
OL,10,Fcentral control of all the Iranian
OL,11,Fmilitias. The process of rebuilding
OL,12,Fconfidence in the security of the
OL,13,FStrait will not be easy.
OL,15,FAnd anyway, production facilities in
OL,16,Fthe Gulf that have been switched off
OL,17,Fcan't be switched on overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FSo, although the business and energy
OL,6,Fdepartments are being reassured by
OL,7,Fchemicals manufacturers and petrol
OL,8,Fretailers and other relevant
OL,9,Fbusinesses that they won't run out of
OL,10,Fvital supplies this week or next, that
OL,11,Fis obvious and of limited utility.
OL,13,FThe economic pain is coming. And the
OL,14,Fonly questions are about severity -
OL,15,Fbad or very bad - and duration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
