FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FThe political point for the PM is it
OL,6,Fis his responsibility to protect the
OL,7,Fliving standards and quality of life
OL,8,Fof British people. And even if our
OL,9,Flooming hardship is largely Trump's
OL,10,Ffault, it's Starmer who will be held
OL,11,Faccountable by voters for whether he
OL,12,Fis protecting them appropriately and
OL,13,Feffectively.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
