OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FIt is worth noting that the massive
OL,6,Frise in the cost of living in the last
OL,7,Fparliament was largely the result of
OL,8,FCovid and Putin's invasion of Ukraine,
OL,9,Fand yet the Tories were massacred at
OL,10,Fthe last election (though of course
OL,11,Fthe incompetence of Truss's mini
OL,12,Fbudget didn't help them).
OL,14,FThis is another way of saying that
OL,15,Fjust as Starmer has acknowledged the
OL,16,FUK has a material interest in keeping
OL,17,Fthe peace in Ukraine, if a ceasefire
OL,18,Fwith Putin is ever agreed, the same
OL,19,Fholds true of the Strait of Hormuz and
OL,20,Fthe UK more generally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FBut if some kind of stability returns
OL,6,Fto the Gulf, and British ships and
OL,7,Fplanes are deployed there to maintain
OL,8,Fthat stability, that will be a
OL,9,Fchallenge to the government - because
OL,10,Fit will seriously deplete military
OL,11,Fresources available for Ukraine's
OL,12,F"coalition of the willing", policing
OL,13,Fthe so-called High North of the Arctic
OL,14,Fand the many other regions vulnerable
OL,15,Fto conflict and instability.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
