OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773907468
OL,3,CTrump's Iran war is changing everything
OL,5,FAnd one other thing: Iran has shown in
OL,6,Fspectacular fashion the damage that
OL,7,Fcan be wreaked with drones. So as
OL,8,Fseveral ministers have said to me with
OL,9,Frising alarm, the UK armed forces own
OL,10,Ftoo few attack drones or counter-drone
OL,11,Fsystems. So-called uncrewed warfare is
OL,12,Fthe new norm, but it is not clear
OL,13,Fwhether the UK armed forces - or the
OL,14,FUS - is ready.
OL,16,F"This war is changing everything," a
OL,17,Fminister said to me, "about the
OL,18,Foutlook for the global economy in the
OL,19,Fshort term, the energy supply chains
OL,20,Fthat we can rely on and how we defend
OL,21,Fourselves in all senses."
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@bO]yD@VOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
